resources: Check your physical activitytext_header To perform the test should take into account those activities that involve a significant physical effort and cause an acceleration of breathing or heart rate in each of the referred environments. Work Activity Does your job require intense physical activity that involves a significant acceleration of breathing or heart rate for at least 10 consecutive minutes? In a typical week, how many days do you do physical activities at work? Name On those days when you do physical activity, how much time in minutes do you usually spend on those activities? Displacement Activity Free Time Activity 30m 60m 120m Do you walk or use a bicycle for at least 10 consecutive minutes on your commute? In a typical week, how many days do you walk or cycle for at least 10 consecutive minutes on your commute? On a typical day, how much time in minutes do you spend walking or cycling to get around? The minimum value of the week is 0 days The maximum value of the week is 7 days It is necessary to select the check of the first question In your free time do you do any activity that implies acceleration of breathing or heart rate for at least 10 consecutive minutes? In a typical week, how many days do you do physical activities in your free time? On those days when you do physical activities in your free time, how much time in minutes do you usually spend on those activities? Check your Physical Activity level PHYSICAL ACTIVITY LEVEL Name: %s BAD NOT GOOD GOOD VERY GOOD EXCELENT Your level of Physical Activity is %s It is necessary to put your name RESET DATA If you select an environment it is necessary to fill in the activity days and select a range of time dedicated to the activity It is necessary to fill some environment + - 0
